CustomField.description: Spanning over 200,000,000 unique emails in the past 12 months, this data identifies active emails within your list. Sourced from trusted mailing partners, this provides the month and year (in YYYY-MM format) we last saw the email “open.” Match rates typically range from 30-40% for U.S. data.
